snippet.title: Deck of Haunts - Teaser #1
snippet.description:
Deck of Haunts is a deck building roguelike where you play as a haunted house, sowing fear and murdering hapless adventurers.
Wishlist here: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3179730/Deck_of_Haunts/
